# PHP dependencies are installed inside the image by `make live` (composer install).
# Excluding vendor/ keeps the build context small on GitHub-hosted runners (~14 GB free disk).
**/vendor/

# Node deps are installed in-container for modules that run `npm install` in `make live`.
**/node_modules/

.git/
.github/
.devcontainer/

# Not used by .resources/Containerfile image builds (see php-build-images matrix).
zmscitizenview/
zmsautomation/

# CI / dev artifacts
**/.cache/
**/.phpunit.result.cache
**/public/_tests/
**/artifacts/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
tags
